Privacy Centre
Your data, your say.
Your data belongs to you, and we promise to treat it that way. You have the right to know what we use it for and why. And even though we love hearing from customers we’ll never contact you without your consent.
No hiding in the small print.
We’re clear and upfront about how we manage your data in the app, on the website and in-store. We’re open and transparent about your privacy rights and show you how to exercise them.
Privacy by design.
Respecting your privacy rights is a primary objective when we develop new products and services. We place customers, and their privacy rights, at the centre of everything we do from design to delivery.
Highest standards
We hold ourselves accountable to the highest data protection standards, and regularly audit how we comply with them, to make sure we’re living up to those standards and our commitment to you.
Keeping your data safe.
We take data security seriously and are fully committed to keeping yours safe. Visit our
security page
to see how we keep prying eyes away from your data.
