Privacy preference centre
We and our partners may collect information from your device for the purposes listed below. To do so, we need your permission. Because we respect your right to privacy, you can choose not to allow cookies (except the ones that are essential to make our site work as it should). Click on the headings below to find out more and manage your settings. You can change your mind at any time by editing your settings in this preference centre again. If you choose to do nothing, no non-essential cookies will be installed.
More information
Accept All
Manage Your Cookie Preferences
Always Active
These cookies and similar technologies make our website work. We use these for important things like security or making the ordering of currency possible. These cookies do not gather any information about you. If we offer a branded service through one of our partners, such as a supermarket or bank, the essential cookies could be both ours and our partners. You may disable these by changing your browser settings, but this may affect how the website functions.
Analytics Cookies
We'd like to set analytics cookies and other tracking technologies to help us to improve our website by collecting information on how you use it (such as which of our webpages are the most popular), or what happens after you interact with our ads on our business partners’ sites (e.g. if you visited this Travelex site after clicking an advert on a partner’s site, we may collect information that tells us if you made a purchase when you visit us). These cookies collect information in a way that does not directly identify anyone. For more detail on how these cookies work, please read our Cookie Statement.
Functionality Cookies
We’d also like to set cookies and other tracking technologies that enable enhanced functionality and personalisation e.g. to remember your language preferences. They may be set by us or by third party providers whose services we have added to our webpages. Without these cookies some or all of these services may not function optimally and you might have to set preferences again on your next visit. For more detail on how these cookies work, please see our Cookie Statement.
Marketing Cookies
These cookies and other tracking technologies may be set on our site by our business or advertising partners. They may be used by those companies to build a profile of your interests and show you relevant adverts on other sites. They do not directly store personal information, but are based on uniquely identifying your browser and device. Without these cookies you may still receive advertising, but it will be less tailored to your interests. For more detail on how these cookies work, please see our Cookie Statement.
